Allow differences in heightTermsGeneral Terms and Conditions of Resin Artattack1 Applicability to entrepreneurs and definitions of terms(1) The following General Terms and Conditions apply to all deliveries between us and a consumer in their version valid at the time of ordering.The consumer is any natural person who concludes a legal transaction for purposes that cannot be attributed primarily to his commercial or independent professional activity (Section 13 of the German Civil Code).2 Conclusion of a contract, storage of the contract text(1) The following terms and conditions for the conclusion of the contract apply to orders placed through my Etsy Shophttps://www.etsy.com/de/shop/ResinArtattack(2) In the event of the conclusion of the contract, the contract shall be concluded withResin Artattackachieved.(3) The presentation of the goods in my internet shop does not constitute a legally binding contract offer on my part, but is only a non-binding request to the consumer to order goods. By ordering the desired goods, the consumer makes a binding offer for him to conclude a purchase contract.The acceptance of the offer shall be made in writing or in text form or by sending the ordered goods within three weeks. After fruitless expiry of the period, the offer is deemed to have been rejected.(4) Upon receipt of an order in my internet shop, the following regulations apply: The consumer makes a binding contract offer by successfully going through the order procedure provided for in my internet shop.The order is made in the following steps:1) Selection of the desired goods2) Confirm by clicking on the "Order" buttons3) Checking the information in the shopping cart4) Actuation of the button "to the checkout"5) Registration in the Internet shop after registration and entering the applicant information (e-mail address and password).6) Re-examination or correction of the respective entered data.7) Binding dispatch of the order by clicking on the button "Order for a fee" or "buy"Before submitting the order in a binding manner, the consumer can return to the website, where the customer's details are recorded and correct input errors or cancel the ordering process by closing the internet browser.(5) Storage of the contract text for orders via my internet shop : I save the contract text. You can find the agb in any offer as well as in my info box.3 Prices, shipping costs, payment, due date(1) The prices quoted include other price components. In addition, there are possible shipping costs.(2) The consumer has the possibility to use all payments accepted by Etsy as in advance, PayPal.(3) If the consumer has chosen the payment in advance, he undertakes to pay the purchase price immediately after the conclusion of the contract.4 Delivery(1) Unless I have clearly stated this in the product description, all offered items will only be made after the order has been received. Delivery is made according to the information in the respective item description. In the case of payment in advance, the deadline for delivery begins to run on the day after the payment order to the bank responsible for the transfer and for all other payment methods on the day after the conclusion of the contract. If the deadline falls on a Saturday, Sunday or public holiday at the place of delivery, the deadline ends on the next working day.(2) The risk of accidental loss and accidental deterioration of the sold item shall not pass to the buyer until the goods are handed over to the buyer, even when the goods are purchased.Section 5 Retention of titleWe reserve ownership of the goods until full payment of the purchase price.Section 6 WarrantyThe statutory warranty regulations apply.Section 7 Contract Language8 Exchange & ReturnAccording to the concrete wording of Section 312 g (2) No. 1 of the German Civil Code (BGB), the statutory right of withdrawal does not exist in the case of contractsfor the supply of goods which are not prefabricated and for the manufacture of which an individual choice or destination by the consumer is decisive or which are clearly tailored to the personal needs of the consumer.Only German is available as the contract language.Status of the General Terms and Conditions Nov.2020Look forward to your visit

name: Kind taucht nach Muschel, Anhänger, 925 Sterling Silber, Gießharz, Unikat, ECHTE Handarbeit
description: Kind taucht nach Muschel, Anhänger, Gießharz, 925 Sterling SilberDie kleinen Mini Muscheln sind echt und ich habe sie selber aus dem Rhein (Fluss) gesammelt.Im Harz sind Glitzerpartikel, die" Algen" sind aus echtem Moos.( Da die Farbe nur bedingt lichtecht ist habe ich den Preis von ursprünglich 115,-Euro auf 75,- Euro gesenkt. Das heißt der Käufer erklärt sich damit einverstanden das das Blau mit der Zeit blasser werden kann!!)Alles von Hand hergestellt! Fassung wie der Stein aus Harz. Dieser wurde in mehreren Schichten hergestellt.Von der Herstellung der Fassung konnte ich aus Platzgründen keine Bilder einstellen. Auch diese ist ein Unikat.Der Anhänger ist bis auf das Figürchen einmalig. Die Figur stammt aus dem Modellbau und ist 1:1 realistisch! (und nicht ganz billig) Dadurch das sie so klein ist und in Harz gegossen erkennt man nicht jedes Detail.Achtung: Farbabweichngen sind durch Kamera und Computerbildschirme gegeben. Je nach Hintergrund kommt der Anhänger durch seine Tranzparenz anders zur Geltung!!! Und der Anhänger leuchtet so natürlich nur in der Sonne. Im Hier war der Guß sehr aufwendig! Es ist auch schwierig und kostet Nerven, aber so spart man sich die Achterbahn fahrt...Inklusive Fassung Material und Zeitaufwand ist der Anhänger sehr, sehr Preisgünstig!!!Der Anhänger kommt mit Kette in Schmuckschachtel mit Zertifikat und ist ein Unikat.Die Herstellung ist aufwendig und kann sich über 3-4 Wochen ziehen!Zuerst denke ich mir etwas aus und ordne es in der Gießform an, das Harz wird natürlich jedes mal angerührt. Die Hälfte wird aufgegossen und nochmal mit Pinzette alles ordentlich platziert,Nach 24 Stunden wird  VORSICHTIG die zweite Schicht aufgegossen bis zur Oberflächenspannung.Dann muss das Harz mindestens eine Woche aushärten.Die Fassung ist von mir von Hand gemacht in dem ich starken Draht in Form gewalzt habe- ebenfalls zeitaufwendig mit zwischen glühen. Dann habe ich den Rand angeschmolzen und die Fassung rund gebogen angepasst und verlötet.  Öse angelötet und die Schlaufe ist ebenfalls Handarbeit.Der Harzanhänger wird angepasst und in die Fassung gedrückt. Diese ist breiter damit ich den Rest aufüllen kann mit noch einer Schicht Harz damit er fest sitzt.Dies ist eine KURZE Zusammenfassung,  es sind weitaus mehr Arbeitsschrichte!!!!! +-+Die Kettenlänge ist bis 50 cm Gratis- schöne stabile 925 Silberkette!Der Anhänger hat ziemlich genau die Größe eines 2 Euro Stückes, ) 2,5 cm.Je nachdem sieht dieser Anhänger besser an einer längeren Kette aus.AB 50 cm mich bitte VOR dem Kauf kontaktieren da ich ab dieser länge einen Aufpreis berechnen muss.In das Harz habe ich einen speziell dafür gemachten UV Schutz gemischt, dieser schützt das Harz vorm vergilben. Der Anhänger kann aber mit einer dafür geeigneten Paste wieder aufpoliert werden.Bei Fragen kann man mich gerne kontaktieren!Gemacht mit Herz <3Versand erfolgt als versichertes Einschreiben Weltweit!(Keine Packstation, und bitte nicht direkt vor dem Urlaub bestellen.)Hinweis: Die Farbe des Wassers ist nur bedingt Lichtecht!!

description: Sun pendant, 925 sterling silver, with 585 gold(Made to order!)I thought for such a trailer is slow time and a nice alternative to other characters....I had hoped it would be a little easier to implement, but it has become quite cumbersome.Since it is handmade, the trailer is not industrially perfect round.Here is some more information about this sign:Sun sign is the symbol of the divine and soul power. From the center, the divine power radiates to the outside.The symbol stands for the sun, Sunday and gold. It is also considered a powerful reinforcement sign, so that positive energies are amplified in all directions.Since the circle has neither beginning nor end, it also stands for infinity.The sun sign reflects the law of reflection and self-knowledge.Trust in yourself and the Divine independent of the outside.Recognition of one's own light and this from the inside (golden circle/point) to radiate /light outwards.It stands for God, the cosmic consciousness and enlightenment.Astrology= for the SunSun sign stands for the number 1Manufacturing process in brief:-Silver plate sawn out, polished and drilled in center hole-pre-polished and eyelet adapted and firmly soldered, polished-with cutter elaborately milled beams, then still with Diamantier file after machined- Self-made 585 gold wire guided through hole-from both sides gold wire with hammer pinned/ flat hammeredMeans the gold is not soldered on the surface,but passes through the silver plate, is forged, i.e. that in this case there is also more gold in the trailer than seen from the front!!!!Small trailer but a lot of work.The pendant comes in jewelry box with certificate!The chain length is included up to 50 cm.Please contact me BEFORE THE BUY if a longer chain is desired, as I have to charge a small extra charge from this length.Shipping takes place as INSURED EInletter worldwide!!!Made with heart! If you have any questions or wishes, please feel free to contact me. :)Dimensions:approx. 1.4 cm

name: Necklace Triskele Triple Spiral Wood Burned
description: Unique men's or ladies wooden necklace.Triple spiral(Druidism): Derived from the Greek word "Triskeles" meaning "three legs", the Triskele or Triple Spiral is a complex ancient Celtic symbol. Often referred to by many as a Triskelion, its earliest creation dates back to the Neolithic era, as it can be seen at the entrance of Newgrange, Ireland. The Triskele gained popularity in its use within the Celtic culture from 500BC onwards. This archaic symbol is one of the most convoluted to decipher as symbolists believe it is reflective of many areas of culture from the time.1)The motion of action, cycles, progress, revolution and competition.2)Life-death-rebirth, spirit-mind-body, mother-father-child, past-present-future, power-intellect-love and creation-preservation-destructionIt’s thought that through the combination of these two areas we gain one meaning of the Celtic triskele. It is believed to represent a tale of forward motion to reach understanding. However, this is thought not to be the only meaning, as it is also believed to represent three Celtic worlds; the spiritual world, the present world and the celestial world. Like the ancient Trinity knot, the number 3 holds a special symbolism within the triskele.Material:Wood: Beech WoodCord:  Cotton Waxed CordVarnish: Odorless Wood Varnish for children's toysApproximate Dimensions:Size:  35mm x 35mm x ~5mmCord Size: AdjustablePlease note that this item is handmade, so there may be small differences comparing with the photo.If you have any inquiries, please don’t hesitate to contact me. For this reason, rose quartz can be recommended for all life situations in which a change or new beginning takes place:Rose Quartz Raw StoneRose Quartz Raw Stonee.g. at birth, puberty, pregnancy, career change, menopause, divorce, euthanasia. With "gentle determination" the rose quartz helps to unfold itself and to realize its true needs.He stands for unconditional love, which is without judging. This includes being able to accept oneself and so the rose quartz can help lonely people to find in themselves the comfort and security that they have been denied in the outside. Rose quartz promotes empathy, which has a beneficial effect, especially in divorces or frequent disputes. Mistrust, fear, hatred and resentment dissolve and enable forgiveness. It makes it easier to accept others and themselves as they are and thus fosters a friendly atmosphere that is characterized by mutual respect. For this purpose, it is best to place a larger rose quartz chunk in the living/dining area or at the workplace. It should also not be missing in any children's room or living room of the elderly! Under the bed, it can help you get a better night's sleep.Just as the rose is the classic flower of love, rose quartz is the stone for all problems in the field of feelings, whether it is self-reproach or lack of respect for others or the environment. To be able to give love, I must first discard the (unconscious) conviction "I am not worth being loved" and begin to love myself. Only then can my love be visible in the outside.Physical effect:Radiaesthetic reviews showed that rose quartz positively affects relatively many frequencies. In particular, its effect in the area of the nervous system and in problems with the heart and blood circulation could be confirmed, probably due to the manganese content. It can be used well after a "mini-nerve collapse" because it supports strengthening and regeneration of nerves and also on the centers of healing, charity and responsibility.It also has frequencies in the area of digestion (feeling full, liver), acts on the skin (nails, warts, adipose tissue), the bone structure and the genital organs.The bracelet is with an elastic stretch band.
